author: Lauren Murphy
title: MusicNews | The Corrs return with comeback single 'Bring on the Night' - hear it now
text:
Like 'em or lump 'em, The Corrs are officially back, (BACK, B CK!!! *jazz hands*)
The Dundalk band debuted their new single - the first release in a decade - 'Bring on the Night' on BBC radio the other morning, and now it's found its way online.
Their comeback album ' White Light' is out on November 27th.
Jim has also been busy tweeting pictures of his siblings in the studio:
